            "title": "美元定期存款利率大比拼 邊間銀行最高息？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"628\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_FpVgc3nGOP_Ew9fcF7FWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyOA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-11/c6d38500-6004-11ed-af6e-40beea945859\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去銀行做美元定期存款，回報雖然未必及得上股票、債券，但勝在夠穩陣，而且簡單易明，加上港元與美元掛鈎，減低匯率風險，難怪不少穩健投資者皆鍾情這種收息工具。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於美元定期年利率較港元定期年利率更優厚，而且港元與美元掛鈎，可減低一般做外幣定期的匯率風險。我們從多間銀行網站搜尋資料，綜合數據以1萬美元及10萬美元作例子，比較一下本港各大銀行最新定期存款利率！利率表更附有各間銀行定期存款優惠連結，方便大家參考！</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b9e15c99-b1a1-4a77-b05e-7ccc69e27971-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩通發表報告，認為美國經濟增長前景穩健，聯儲局很難大舉減息。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告稱，美國經濟基礎穩固，即使沃什就任聯儲局主席後，亦很難左右聯邦公開市場委員會的運作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於本周公布的非農就業數據較預期強，目前交易員已放棄6月減息的預測，改為預計聯儲局將在7月減息四分一厘，並在年底前再次減息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>延伸閱讀：</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩通：美國經濟穩健 聯儲局難大規模減息;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%91%A9%E9%80%9A-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%A9%A9%E5%81%A5-%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E5%B1%80%E9%9B%A3%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF-031140665.html\"><strong>摩通：美國經濟穩健 聯儲局難大規模減息</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:避險大亨重押黃金 預言聯儲局今年減息遠超過兩次;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E9%81%BF%E9%9A%AA%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%A8%E9%87%8D%E6%8A%BC%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E8%8F%AF%E8%A8%B1%E9%A0%98%E5%B0%8E%E4%B8%8Bfed%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E9%81%A0%E8%B6%85%E9%81%8E%E5%85%A9%E6%AC%A1-035004008.html\"><strong>避險大亨重押黃金 預言聯儲局今年減息遠超過兩次</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普稱讚1月非農就業強勁 再度呼籲大幅減息;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E8%AE%9A1%E6%9C%88%E9%9D%9E%E8%BE%B2%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81-%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-004219325.html\"><strong>特朗普稱讚1月非農就業強勁 再度呼籲大幅減息</strong></a></p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港銀行方面，富邦下調6個月和12個月美元定存5點子。</p><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, 176%)\"></div></blockquote><iframe height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://flo.uri.sh/visualisation/22086444/embed?auto=1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1.42\" title=\"Flourish chart\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>",
